message.text:
Hi! Just in case the owner is here, please help me get in touch with them. 

We found two cards — a room key card and a debit card — at around 2:26 AM today (Wednesday, September 17) along P. Campa Street near Soy & Sesame. If these belong to you or someone you know, please reach out to me for verification and return! 🙇🏻‍♀️
